Title: Find Me Falling
Produced by: Stelana Kliris Keith Arnold Steven Shapiro
Starring: Harry Connick Jr. Agni Scott Ali Fumiko Whitney
Production companies: Jupiter Peak Productions Meraki Films Das Films
Production: Filming began in Cyprus in May 2022.  Filming specifically occurred in Pegeia and Nicosia.  In November 2022, it was announced that the film was entering the final stage of production.
